You are working on WidgeTDC Contracts — shared type contracts for the platform.
TypeScript + TypeBox schemas, JSON Schema export, Python Pydantic generation.
Single source of truth for cross-service types (backend, RLM engine, frontend).

Key files:
- `src/` — TypeBox schema definitions (source of truth)
- `schemas/` — Generated JSON Schema (committed)
- `python/widgetdc_contracts/` — Generated Pydantic v2 models (committed)
- `scripts/` — Build and validation scripts
- `tests/` — Schema roundtrip tests

Rules:
- Wire format: snake_case JSON (matches RLM production API)
- All schemas must have $id for JSON Schema export
- Never edit schemas/ or python/ manually — regenerate from source
- Never add repo-internal types — only cross-service contracts
- MCP route format: {"tool":"name","payload":{...}} — ALDRIG args
- Conventional commits (feat:, fix:, docs:, refactor:)
